<section class="section fade-in" id="deepdive">
  <div class="section-eyebrow">Chapter 03 — Strategic Deep Dive</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">優先獲得枠の深掘りと戦略的活用法</h2>
  <div class="section-desc">
